	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmmmm, while the shield of thistles is a nice proc, especially when soloing, I would say make the trade.&nbsp;&nbsp;I don't know the value of the Tower Blade but the speed is SIGNIFICANTLY better!  I would bet you will for more damage over the course of a battle, than you will with the 2-H Prac Sword.  Your individual hits won't look as good so you have to keep that in mind, but you should do more damage in the long run due to increased opportunities!<br><br>And, in this game as a semi-tank, Armor Class is king! The extra 5 AC won't hurt either.  Just my opinion. I'm sure others may disagree. But if it were me, I'd make the trade.<br><br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>32nd Circle of Dwarven Paladins<br>Twilight Brethren<br>&nbsp;<br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Knight<br>Torvonnilous Server<br><br>"Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness"</td></tr>
