	   <tr><td colspan=2>for those of you that want to know. this is how i find to kill mobs the fastest when in a group. first of all stand on other side of mob then the other tanks. be they a warrior, rogue, ranger, whatever taunt your heart away. this makes the mob face you and the other tanks can do more damage from behind. above lvl i dont know if this still works but from lvl 20 to 30 (after the damage cap is lifted) it works great. hopefully this helps yall out i find we all take less damage this way and the mob tends to go down in 30 to 60 sec. plus this way the healer of the group does not have to heal everyone just you. <br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
