	   <tr><td colspan=2><br><br>Celtpirate is correct. The attack from the back is the best battle tact in a group. I found this out in High Keep, fighting in the guard room. I usually let the tanks pull the monsters. After the shout of INC., I hit the yaulp, then quickly go around the mob and backstab the monster that the puller or pullers are attacking and wear the taunt key out. By doing this it reduces damage for the group and kills monsters faster. NOTE: When attacking,always get the monster the puller is attacking. <br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
