	   <tr><td colspan=2>hot keys and hints:<br>%t target<br>%s sex<br>%r race<br>so you can get fancy with it (the race one does not work with all mobs..dont know if it is broken or what)<br><br>/book opens spell book and you start medding<br>/book # opens book to that page<br><br>/spell # is how you cast a spell with you clicking on the gem. (# 1 - 8) this is how the above did yaulp and stun.<br>alt1-8 also does this <br><br>F1-8 is everyone in your group ( i think most people know that but for those that dont it can be usefull, you can also just click on there name in the group box.)<br><br>remember you have 10 pages of hotkeys use them add in things to make you stand out:<br>you will not turn your back on me %t<br>/taunt<br><br>or<br>may marr stop all your movement<br>/spell 2 (this being stun or root)<br><br>whatever have fun with it just no emotes as they cause lag :)<br><br>oh well all i can think of now have fun<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
