lass is concerned I think we are pretty much even.  Of course I would wanna see more paladin specific weapons and stuff.  If there is one complain, I think that Ghoulbane should be a no drop.  Too many non-Paladins are camping at Lord Shin's place just so they can sell our priced possesion. <br><br>Well,that is my opinion and I know you're also entitled to your own opinion as well. All I'm asking is think about what your asking.  <br><br>The last thing I wanna see when i play this game is everyone playing the same class.  That would really suck!<br><br><br>Good Journey<br>Fellow Paly<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
