	   <tr><td colspan=2>I wholeheartedly say HELL YEAH to SOuldragoon's post. The only problem you might have is getting a group to go camp the Bedroom/spider room. The exp is amazing with a full group, even at 38, its insane. At 35(Hell level) its GREAT exp, better than soloing high blues in Unrest. not that great loot in the spider room, but you will be safe from trains and the exp is amazing. Youll never want to leave, you get to know people and make more friends, which means more grouping later. WARNING- Do NOT pull the greater ice bone skellies unless you have a healer/enchanter. You can even break into the room with 3 poeple as long as one can heal/ do crowd control. Best exp ever heh.<br>Zomor-bertoxx<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
