	   <tr><td colspan=2>I use a blackened iron bastard sword for 2H Slash. It was a gift to me, but I read it drops off a goblin in Runneyeye.&nbsp;&nbsp;Using it, I hit at my under 20 level max of 29. <br><br>For 1HB, I use the Shining Star of Light (28/6), its from a Cleric/Paladin quest and I consider it to be the first paladin holy weapon.  I haven't really been looking for another one yet, Im at level 15 and more intersted in a 1HS.<br><br>So looking through Allakhazam's, I found these 1HS I'm interested in.  I currently use a forged long sword (6/28), so these had to be better than this one, most important to me was the delay and possibly being magical.<br><br>So as I said earlier, I got my first Paladin Holy Weapon.  It's time to get my second, the Falchion of Koada'Vie (6/24)MAGIC LORE ITEM. But without a group, me at lvl 16, may need to get some more exp first.<br><br>Other Options:<br>Gladius(7/29)MAGIC- Dropped from the Lessor Blade Fiend at the Estate of Undead.  This guy shows up randomly so there isn't a camp for it.  The place is just kinda bad news for lvl 17, but is doable.<br><br>Polished Granite Tomahawk (6/26) MAGIC LORE ITEM - Dropped in Highhold Pass on the gnoll Grenix Mucktail.  He spawns rarely on the gnoll ledge, so I heard.  This one has a beserker strength proc.  The Dwarvish Axe (6/26)may be an easier cheaper alternative, but it isn't magical or have the proc bonus.  The Dwarvish Axe can be obtained from a quest or Lord Darish in Crushbone(lvl17).<br><br>Barbed Leather Whip (7/28) MAGIC - can be obtained from Bonecracker in Najena (lvl 22)<br><br>Coldian Velium Long Sword (7/28) MAGIC Purchased from vendors in Velious<br><br>Except for not being magical, the racial crafted swords are really good.  Antonian Long Sword (8/28), Seafarer's Cutlass (7/23) and Koada'Dal Falchion (7/24) have rocking stats.  Im not sure if the Seafarer's Cutlass can be made anymore.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>This is the way, grasshopper.</td></tr>
